\c 24
\s Jobho anonyunyuta kuti Mwari haacherekedzi vakaipa
\p
\v 1 Sei nguva\x + Mup. 9.12. Isa. 13.22. Jer. 27.7. Eze. 22.3. 30.3.\x* dzisina kuvanzirwa Wemasimbaose\x + 15.20.\x*, uye vanomuziva vasingaoni\x + 18.21.\x* mazuva ake\x + 18.20. Isa. 13.6,9. Jow. 1.15. 2.1.\x*?
\v 2 Vanoshandura miganhu\x + Det. 19.14.\x*; vanopamba mapoka emakwai vachi\add a\add*fudza.
\v 3 Vanotinha mbongoro yenherera\x + Isa. 20.4.\x*; vanotora nzombe yechirikadzi kuita rubatso\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 4 Vanotsausa vanoshaiwa kubva panzira\x + Amo. 2.7. 5.12.\x*; varombo venyika\x + Map. 76.9. Zef. 2.3.\x* vanovanda pamwe\x + 30.5,6. Zvir. 28.28.\x*.
\v 5 Tarira, imbongoro dzemusango murenje\x + 6.5.\x*, vanobudira kubasa ravo\x + Map. 104.23.\x*, vachitsvaka chijimbiwa\x + Map. 104.21.\x* nekushingaira\x + Map. 63.1.\x*; renje rive zvekudya zvake \add ne\add*zvevana.
\v 6 Mumunda vanokohwa mashanga ake, vanofuhurudza munda wemizambiringa wewakaipa.
\v 7 Vanorara usiku vakashama vasina zvipfeko, uye vasina chifukidzo muchando.
\v 8 Vakanyorova nekupfunha kwemakomo\x + 8.16.\x*, uye vanobatirira pabwe nekuda kwekushaiwa utiziro\x + Marir. 4.5.\x*.
\v 9 Vanobvuta nherera pazamu, nekutora rubatso pamurombo\x + 22.6.\x*.
\v 10 Vanofamba vakashama\x + 30.28. Map. 38.6. 104.26. 131.1. Marir. 5.18.\x* vasina chipfeko\x + 24.7. 31.19.\x*, uye vane nzara vanotakura chisote\x + Jak. 5.4.\x*.
\v 11 Pakati pemasvingo vanosvina mafuta\x + Jak. 5.4.\x*, vanotsika zvisviniro zvewaini, asi vane nyota\x + Vato. 9.27. Isa. 63.2,3. Marir. 1.15.\x*.
\v 12 Vanhu vanogomera vari muguta\x + Eze. 30.24. Jer. 51.52.\x*, uye mweya wevakakuvadzwa unochema\x + Eze. 30.24. Jer. 51.52.\x*; asi Mwari haa\add va\add*verengeri kusarurama\x + 1.22.\x*.
\v 13 Ndivo vari pakati pevanomukira chiedza; havazivi nzira dzake, uye havagari pamakwara ake\x + Joh. 3.19,20.\x*.
\v 14 Muurayi anomuka pamambakwedza, anouraya murombo neanoshaiwa; uye pausiku wakaita sembavha.
\v 15 Zisowo remhombwe rinomirira rubvunzavaeni, ichiti: Hakuna ziso richandiona; ndokuisa chifukidzo pachiso.
\v 16 Murima vanochera nemudzimba \add dza\add*vanoisa mucherekedzo masikati; havazivi chiedza.
\v 17 Nokuti pamwechete mangwanani irima rerufu kwavari; nokuti vanoziva zvityiso zvemumvuri werufu.
\v 18 Wakareruka pachiso chemvura; mugove wavo wakatukwa panyika; haatendeuki panzira yeminda yemizambiringa.
\v 19 Kuoma nekupisa kunopedza mvura yemagada echando, \add saizvozvo\add* Sheori vakatadza.
\v 20 Chizvaro chichamukanganwa; honye dzichatapirirwa naye; haachazorangarirwizve; neuipi huchagurwa semuti.
\v 21 Iye unodya mhanje isingabereki; uye haaitiri chirikadzi zvakanaka.
\v 22 Uye anokweva vane simba nesimba rake; anomuka, uye haana chokwadi neupenyu\x + Map. 76.5.\x*.
\v 23 Anomupa kuchengetedzeka, paanosendama, asi meso ake ari pamusoro penzira dzavo\x + 10.3. Map. 11.4.\x*.
\v 24 Vanokudzwa kwechinguvana, ndokuva vasipo; vachideredzwa; vanovharirwa sevese\x + Map. 37.10.\x*; uye semusoro wehura yezviyo\x + Vato. 12.6.\x* vanogurwa\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino kana zvisina kudaro, ndiani angandiita murevi wenhema, aite nhauro yangu ishaye maturo\x + 9.24.\x*?